This is a project to host the latest mutt-sidebar patch for mutt 1.5.22.
The goal of this repository is to maintain a patch that is applicable the Homebrew [1] mutt package.

The patch itself is derived from the sidebar patch [2] from the FreeBSD Ports [3].

[1] https://github.com/mxcl/homebrew
[2] http://www.freebsd.org/cgi/query-pr.cgi?pr=183251
[3] http://svnweb.freebsd.org/ports/head/mail/mutt/files/extra-patch-sidebar?view=log
